{"tid":88440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"To Backup閪：我唔熟達哥亦唔係達哥忠實粉絲","createTime":"2017-01-20T15:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T16:21:57.000Z","uid":2569,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b06e6500ae478ce3b5d297ac439e793187ba2032","tid":88440,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:20:48.000Z","msg":"我前半年先開始睇佢既直播<br />\n睇完佢出既聲明我起字裡行間感受到佢個種<br />\n委屈，同埋忍唔住要爆既憤怒。究竟點樣先可以迫到一個人講得出呢啲說話去澄清件事...<br />\n我唔明點解有人講得出咁啲荒謬既野：如果唔係backup佬達哥就唔會紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係達哥出直播你有得Backup？</span><br />\n佢唔紅你Back來做乜，唔紅無人睇你Backup都哂鳩氣啦，唔好同佢講你Backup佢無目的囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，係都要迫當時人出聲明講心底話爆柒你班仆街先安樂。<br />\n好撚簡單一樣野，即刻停止Backup同埋自動收皮，出道歉聲明同嘔返哂啲錢出來！<br />\n唔係你以為起背後做咁多手動作，挑起事端生仔會有屎忽，無後果？"},{"pid":"6059dacd67e1e3b760ae65adac8829d28bdba6ff","tid":88440,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e462c1dfffa78b4510937ac960637653c6396032","tid":88440,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6150153a767ddcf74f99ff37d256550e33e620","tid":88440,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c604cbdaa49aa2245f14723b51a18eb2370b21","tid":88440,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"Hello Backup鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea946654e593dec84ea9d9579cbc26c69607181"